&lt;p&gt;The exam covers a variety of topics, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-adapters"&gt;Contributing to Meshery Adapters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/extensibility/ui"&gt;Meshery UI Extensibility&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/extensibility/authorization"&gt;Authorization Extensibility&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/extensibility/api"&gt;Using Meshery APIs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/extensibility/providers"&gt;Local and Remote Providers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Meshery Models Contributor Exam</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-models/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-models/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Meshery Models examination verifies contributor understanding of one of Meshery&amp;rsquo;s core architectural components and is one of a set of mandatory exams comprising the Certified Meshery Contributor certification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The exam covers a variety of topics, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-models-quick-start"&gt;Contributing to Models Quick Start&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-models"&gt;Contributing to Meshery Models&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-components"&gt;Contributing to Model Components&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-relationships"&gt;Contributing to Model Relationships&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-policies"&gt;Contributing to Meshery Policies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supplemental topics:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/concepts/logical/models"&gt;Concepts of Meshery Models&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Meshery Server Contributor Exam</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-server/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-server/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Meshery Server examination verifies contributor understanding of one of Meshery&amp;rsquo;s core architectural components and is one of a set of mandatory exams comprising the Certified Meshery Contributor certification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This exam focuses on the candidate&amp;rsquo;s ability to contribute to the Meshery Server codebase. The exam covers a variety of topics, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-server"&gt;Contributing to Meshery Server&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-server-events"&gt;Contributing to Meshery Server Events&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-error"&gt;How to write MeshKit Compatible Errors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/build-and-release"&gt;Build &amp;amp; Release (CI)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-schemas"&gt;Schema-driven development in Meshery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This exam does not cover Meshery Server usage, but focuses on Meshery Server contribution. For information on using Meshery Server, please refer to the &lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io"&gt;Meshery Documentation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Meshery UI Contributor Exam</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-ui/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/certifications/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/certified-meshery-contributor/meshery-ui/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Meshery UI examination verifies contributor understanding of one of Meshery&amp;rsquo;s core architectural components and is one of a set of mandatory exams comprising the Certified Meshery Contributor certification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui"&gt;Contributing to Meshery UI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui-notification-center"&gt;Contributing to Meshery UI - Notification Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui-schemas"&gt;Schema-Driven UI Development in Meshery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui-sistent"&gt;Contributing to Meshery UI - Sistent&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui-tests"&gt;Contributing to Meshery UI End-to-End Tests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io/project/contributing/contributing-ui-widgets"&gt;Contributing to Meshery UI - Dashboard Widgets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This exam does not cover Meshery UI usage, but focuses on Meshery UI contribution. For information on using Meshery UI, please refer to the &lt;a href="https://docs.meshery.io"&gt;Meshery Documentation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Module Quiz</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/learning-paths/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/example-learning-path/course-1/module/quiz/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/learning-paths/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/example-learning-path/course-1/module/quiz/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Module Quiz</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/learning-paths/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/example-learning-path/course-2/module/quiz/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/meshery-academy/pr-preview/pr-94/learning-paths/c5ada327-8a58-4c8a-b9fa-51b95696488c/example-learning-path/course-2/module/quiz/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>